@host = https://localhost:44350

### Register a new user (Bearer tokens, no cookies)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register?useCookies=false
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!",
  "confirmPassword": "P@ssw0rd!"
}

### Login (get access_token)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login?useCookies=false
Content-Type: application/json

email=user@example.com&password=P@ssw0rd!&rememberMe=false

### Copy access_token from login response here:
@access_token = REPLACE_ME

### Call a protected endpoint
GET {{host}}/api/videos
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}